OL,5,G0400 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,6,     FThe news team achieves its
OL,7,     Fultimate aim and, as well as
OL,8,     Fgetting a late extension to the
OL,9,     Fbar, they secure an interview with
OL,10,     Fthe Prime Minister
OL,11,G0430 Stereo Underground
OL,12,     FRichard Latto presents alternative
OL,13,     Fanthems from a music community
OL,14,     Fwith attitude.
OL,15,G0530 Jack Hargreaves' Old Country
OL,16,     FJack Hargreaves is stocking his
OL,17,     Friver with native brown trout. He
OL,18,     Flaments the widespread loss of
OL,19,     Fponds in the countryside, but
OL,20,     Ffinds one that is thriving.
